      • uiReadyCatastropheZone

        public static CatastropheZoneBuilder uiReadyCatastropheZone()
        Returns a catastrophe zone builder with the following fields set
        • Catastrophe: if used via catastropheBuilder.withPeril(), or if onCatastrophe() is called explicitly then the given catastrophe will be used. Otherwise a new UI ready catastrophe will be created
        • Country: US
        • ZoneType: state
        • Code: CA
        Returns:
        a new CatastropheZoneBuilder
